"<div><button>Preview</button><button>Write</button></div><div><span><span><span contenteditable="false"></span></span></span><span><article><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><header><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><h1><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">Understanding </span></span></span><span><strong><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">Nested HTML</span></span></span></span></strong></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> Structures</span></span></span></span></h1></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><p><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"></span></span></span><span><small><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">Published on </span></span></span><span><time><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">November 13, 2025</span></span></span></span></time></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"></span></span></span></span></small></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"></span></span></span></span></p></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span></span></header></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">

</span></span></span><span><section><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><h2><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">Introduction</span></span></span></span></h2></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><p><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">This is a </span></span></span><span><em><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">comprehensive example</span></span></span></span></em></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> of </span></span></span><span><strong><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">nested HTML tags</span></span></span></span></strong></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> working together. The </span></span></span><span><code><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">MarkedInput</span></span></span></span></code></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> library can parse and render </span></span></span><span><mark><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">complex HTML structures</span></span></span></span></mark></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> with multiple levels of nesting.</span></span></span></span></p></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">

</span></span></span><span><blockquote><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span><span><p><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">HTML nesting allows us to create </span></span></span><span><strong><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">rich, semantic documents</span></span></span></span></strong></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> that are both </span></span></span><span><em><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">readable</span></span></span></span></em></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false"> and </span></span></span><span><u><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">well-structured</span></span></span></span></u></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">.</span></span></span></span></p></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span></span></blockquote></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
</span></span></span></span></section></span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">

</span></span></span><span><section><span><span><span><span contenteditable="false">
